		)
		(uuid "5c8fafe0-0038-4221-adcf-0969dcf96310")
	)
	(text_box "!!! CAUTION !!!\n\nVDD5 must remain between 4.5V and 5.5V.\n\nThe switchable analog voltage range is from -20V to +20V. To achieve the maximum number of switching operations, the maximum switchable current is 200mA, at which point the on-resistance (Ron) may rise to as much as 100mΩ over time"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
